tex\">Tracker exchange spec: [http://www.bittorrent.org/beps/bep_0028.html BEP 28]</ref>\n! Remote control via web\n! [[BitTorrent (protocol)#Indexing|Search engine]]\n! Auto updates\n! Reviews and Comments\n! Notes\n|-\n| [[ABC (Yet Another BitTorrent Client)|ABC]]\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes2}} Separate download\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n|\n|-\n| [[Acquisition (software)|Acquisition]]\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n|\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| 3 torrents max, infinite when registered\n|-\n| [[BitComet]]\n| {{yes}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes}}<ref>Supports the [http://www.getright.com/seedtorrent.html Getright Webseeding spec] since v1.14, see [http://wiki.bitcomet.com/Making_torrents_with_BitComet#Web_Seeding BitComet Wiki]</ref>\n| {{beta}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}<ref group=Note>Called [http://wiki.bitcomet.com/preview_while_downloading \"preview mode\"]</ref>\n| {{yes}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes}}\n|{{partial|Built-in Web browser}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{no}}\n| Portable version available\n|-\n| [[BitLet]]\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{no}}\n|\n|-\n| [[BitLord]]\n| {{yes}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{partial|Partial <ref name=\"bep19_webseeding__not_support_http_redirection\" group=Note>Does not support [[List of HTTP status codes#3xx Redirection|HTTP redirection]] (status codes: 301, 302, 303, 307).</ref><ref name=\"bep19_webseeding__not_support_https\" group=Note>Does not support [[HTTPS]].</ref>}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{partial|Built-in Web browser}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{no}}\n|\n|-\n| [[BitTornado]]\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes2}} via [[package management system|PMS]]\n| {{no}}\n|\n|-\n| [[BitTorrent (sof