 has a feed aggregator that displays feeds like emails.</ref>\n<ref name=Shareaza>Maximum active torrent number depends on respective user settings and is limited to 31.</ref>\n}}\n\n\n=== Vulnerabilities ===\nThis comparison of unpatched publicly known vulnerabilities in latest stable version clients is based on vulnerabilities reports by [http://www.securityfocus.com/ SecurityFocus] and [https://secunia.com/ Secunia]. See [[Computer security#unpatched|computer security]] for more details about the importance of unpatched known flaws.\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 85%; text-align:center; width: auto;\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"3\" | BitTorrent client\n! colspan=\"6\" | Known unpatched vulnerabilities\n|-\n! colspan=\"5\" | Secunia !! SecurityFocus\n|-\n!style=\"width:12em\"|Extremely critical<br />(number / oldest)!!style=\"width:12em\"|Highly critical<br />(number / oldest)!!style=\"width:12em\"|Moderately critical<br />(number / oldest)!!style=\"width:12em\"|Less critical<br />(number / oldest)!!style=\"width:12em\"|Not critical<br />(number / oldest)!!style=\"width:12em\"|Total<br />(number / oldest)\n|-\n| [[BitComet]]\n| {{Good|}}[https://secunia.com/product/19152/ 0]\n| {{Good|}}[https://secunia.com/product/19152/ 0]\n| {{Good|}}[https://secunia.com/product/19152/ 0]\n| {{Good|}}[https://secunia.com/product/19152/ 0]\n| {{Good|}}[https://secunia.com/product/19152/ 0]\n| {{Good|}}[http://www.securityfocus.com/cgi-bin/index.cgi?c=12&vendor=BitComet&title=BitComet&version=%201.20 0]\n|-\n| [[BitLord]]\n| {{Good|}}[https://secunia.com/product/7578/ 0]\n| {{Good|}}[https://secunia.com/product/7578/ 0]\n| {{Good|}}[https://secunia.com/product/7578/ 0]\n| {{Good|}}[https://secunia.com/product/7578/ 0]\n| {{Good|}}[https://secunia.com/product/7578/ 0]\n| {{unk| }}[http://www.securityfocus.com/ Unknown]\n|-\n| [[BitTornado]]\n| {{Good|}}[https://secunia.com/product/27087/ 0]\n| {{Good|}}[https://secunia.com/product/27087/ 0]\n| {{Good|}}[https://secunia.com/produ