tps://secunia.com/product/15874/ 0]\n| {{Good|}}[https://secunia.com/product/15874/ 0]\n| {{Good|}}[https://secunia.com/product/15874/ 0]\n| {{Bad| }}[http://www.securityfocus.com/cgi-bin/index.cgi?c=12&vendor=Xunlei&title=Thunder&version=5.7.4%20.401 1]<br />[http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/26536 {{Start date and age|df=yes|2007|11|17|br=yes}}]\n|-\n! rowspan=\"3\" | BitTorrent client\n!Extremely critical<br />(number / oldest)!!Highly critical<br />(number / oldest)!!Moderately critical<br />(number / oldest)!!Less critical<br />(number / oldest)!!Not critical<br />(number / oldest)!!Total<br />(number / oldest)\n|-\n! colspan=\"5\" | Secunia !! SecurityFocus\n|-\n! colspan=\"6\" | Known unpatched vulnerabilities\n|}\n\n== Libraries ==\n; General\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width: 100%; text-align: center; font-size: smaller; table-layout: fixed;\"\n|-\n! BitTorrent library\n! First public release date\n! Latest stable\n! [[Software license]]\n|-\n| [[libtorrent]] (Rasterbar)\n| {{start date and age|df=yes|2005|09|08}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sourceforge.net/projects/libtorrent/files/ |title=libtorrent \u2013 Browse Files at |publisher=Sourceforge.net |date=21 March 2010 |accessdate=15 August 2012}}</ref>\n| {{Latest stable software release/libtorrent}}\n| {{free|[[Free software]]}}\n|-\n| [[MonoTorrent]]\n| {{start date and age|df=yes|2006|09}}\n| {{Latest stable release/MonoTorrent}}\n| {{free|Free software}}\n|-\n| [[rTorrent]] (libTorrent Rakshasa)\n| {{start date and age|df=yes|2004|07|15}}<ref name=\"rakshasa-timeline\">{{cite web |url=http://libtorrent.rakshasa.no/timeline |title=Timeline \u2013 The libTorrent and rTorrent Project |publisher=Libtorrent.rakshasa.no |date=15 July 2012 |accessdate=15 August 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104110338/http://libtorrent.rakshasa.no/timeline |archive-date=4 November 2013 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n| {{Latest stable software release/rTorrent}}\n| {{free|Free software}}\n|-\n|- cl